divs: Sighting DetailsMy wife and I went to Washington D.C. for vacation at the end of May. On May 30th, I took a picture of the statue of Andrew Jackson. On June 26th, 2009, I was showing the picture to a friend of mine (Scott Huff), and we noticed an odd object above the statue. When we zoomed in, we were unable to identify what the object actually is. It resembles a classic UFO shape and Scott suggested I send the picture to you for closer observation. I don't know what it is and I don't remember it when I took the picture, so I would appreciate any feedback you can give me as to what this might be. Thank you.
Summary: Looking at vacation pictures and noticed an odd object.
